{"type": "article", "id": 29170, "title": "带翅膀的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-05T22:53:27Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160705212604RsP489NJDlpYmLCX.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>没有灯罩的保护，只有两根电线随意连接着圆盘底座和带翼的灯泡，看上去就好像一只试图挣脱束缚自由飞翔的鸟，它的名字 Lucellino 也正是由意大利语中小鸟（uccellino）和光（luce）这两个词组合而成 。由 <a href=\"https://www.ingo-maurer.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ingo Maurer</a> 最早于 1992 年设计制作的灯具系列 Lucellino 推出了改良版本 <a href=\"https://www.ingo-maurer.com/en/products/lucellino-led\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lucellino LED</a>，采用的 LED 灯泡 TRI-R 是设计师本人和日本东芝沟通后专门为灯具所打造的，和其他款式相比光芒更自然柔和。除此之外，灯具的底座还加入了触控式的调光器。这是它的<a href=\"https://shop.ingo-maurer.com/en/lucellino-led/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 490 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705212627IJzVea2jQ0DB839t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544466\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705212627v2COTn0LBWYKcfQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705212628ijZkCAReglSbc1LJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.315789\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705212628djWGg4L1xHQSZrhV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}